# Tetris

This is an implementation of tetris that runs in the browser using emscripten and as a standalone window based application.

### TODO

#### Development Features

- [ ] Figure out how to put breakpoints with nvim

#### Learn-checklist

- [ ] Learn how to use cmake to do the bare minimum compilation
- [ ] Learn how to use Vulkan
- [ ] Learn how to bind javascript to webassembly

### System Requirements

1. `bash`
1. `make`
1. `cmake`

### Building

#### From the CLI

1. Open your terminal of choice that supports bash
1. Run `./build.sh console`

